Modulos libreria.¶


func_addition(num1, num2)¶

This functions makes the addition of the numbers num1 and num2.

Parameters:
  • num1 (float) – First addend.
  • num2 (float) – Second addend.
Returns:

Addition.
Return type:

float

Where:

Addition = num1 + num2

func_subtraction(num1, num2)¶

This functions makes the subtraction of the numbers num1 and num2.

Parameters:
  • num1 (float) – Minuend.
  • num2 (float) – Subtrahend.
Returns:

Difference.
Return type:

float

Where:

Difference = num1 - num2
